        },
        {
          "character": "渔丈人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个——日后你我相逢之时，你唤我渔丈人，我唤你芦中人也就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，渔丈人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔丈人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "芦中人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "渔丈人 （同笑） 啊哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "多蒙渡我把江过，"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "日后当报这恩德。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（伍员下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔丈人",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "可叹将军涉风波。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（伍员上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "再与老丈把话说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔丈人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军，为何去而复转？"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈，非是我去而复转，后面倘有追兵，莫说伍员打此经过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔丈人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！老汉偌大年纪，冒着风险将他渡过江来，不料他反而疑我。万一后"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔丈人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "面追兵将他拿住，必说是我泄漏，岂不以德为怨！也罢，我不免投到江中，也"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔丈人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好叫他安心而去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔丈人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊将军，那边追兵来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "伍员",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔丈人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在那里！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（渔丈人投江，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伍员 （扑灯蛾牌） 老丈丧江河、丧江河，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不由人珠泪落！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一定报恩德、报恩德！"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔丈人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈投江一死，不免将篷索砍断，以防不测。"
        }
      ],
